==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infertile
<hw>In*fer"tile</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>infertilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>infertile</ets>. See <er>In-</er>
not, and <er>Fertile</er>.]</ety> <def>Not fertile; not productive;
barren; sterile; unable to propagate its kind; <as>as, an
<ex>infertile</ex> soil</as>; an <ex>infertile</ex> hybrid; -- of living
things and of soil or land.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infertilely</ent>⟦br⟧
